question.title: After migrating to hibernate 6 and spring boot 3, he .transform() not work
question.body:
I migrate my project to hibernate 6.5.3.Final + querydsl:5.1.0 and I can't do transform on querydsl

I have class:

public class Test{
    private final EntityPath<SomeEntity> path;
    private final Querydsl querydsl;

    public Test(EntityManager entityManager) {
        this.path = SimpleEntityPathResolver.INSTANCE.createPath(SomeEntity.class);
        querydsl = new Querydsl(entityManager, new PathBuilder<SomeEntity>(this.path.getType(), this.path.getMetadata()));
    }
}

And method:

private Page<SomeObject> findAllSomeObject(JPQLQuery<?> query, Pageable pageable) {

    List<SomeObject> result = query
            .select(someExpression)
            .transform(GroupBy.groupBy(id)
                    .list(Projections.constructor(SomeObject.class, someExpression))
            );

    return PageableExecutionUtils.getPage(result, pageable, () -> totalCount);
}

While I do .transform() I get error.

Add: below is the full string trace when an exception is received, it is triggered on the call .transform(GroupBy.groupBy(id)):
